<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 1483/98 of 10 July 1998 fixing the actual production of olive oil and the unit amount of production aid for the 1996/97 marketing year </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 1483/98, milles m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks oliivi&otilde;li tegelik toodang ja tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta 1996/97. turustusaastaks 10. juuli 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 136/66/EEC of 22 September 1966 on the establishment of a common organisation of the market in oils and fats (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1581/96 (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. septembri 1966. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kehtestamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1581/96, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 of 17 July 1984 laying down general rules on the granting of aid for the production of olive oil and of aid to olive oil producer organisations (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 636/95 (4), and in particular Article 17a(3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 17. juuli 1984. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84, milles s&auml;testatakse oliivi&otilde;li tootmiseks antava abi ja oliivi&otilde;li tootjate organisatsioonidele antava abi &uuml;ldised eeskirjad, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 636/95, (4) eriti selle artikli 17a l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 of Regulation No 136/66/EEC provides that the unit amount of the production aid must be reduced where the actual production for a given marketing year exceeds the maximum guaranteed quantity fixed for that marketing year; whereas, however, producers whose average production is less than 500 kilograms of olive oil per marketing year are not affected by that reduction; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; artiklis 5 s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra &uuml;hiku kohta peab v&auml;hendama, kui asjaomase turustusaasta tegelik toodang &uuml;letab selle turustusaasta jaoks kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud garanteeritud maksimumkogust; siiski ei m&otilde;juta see v&auml;hendamine tootjaid, kelle keskmine toodang on v&auml;iksem kui 500 kilogrammi oliivi&otilde;li turustusaasta kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 17a of Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84 provides that, in order to determine the unit amount of the production aid for olive oil which may be paid in advance, the estimated production for the marketing year concerned should be established; whereas, for the 1996/97 marketing year, the estimated production aid which may be paid in advance was fixed by Commission Regulation (EC) No 1979/97 (5); </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 artiklis 17a s&auml;testatakse, et oliivi&otilde;li ettemakstava tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;ra kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks &uuml;hiku kohta tuleks kehtestada asjaomase turustusaasta hinnanguline toodang; 1996/97. turustusaasta t&otilde;en&auml;oline tootmistoetus, mida v&otilde;ib ette maksta, on kindlaks m&auml;&auml;ratud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1979/97; (5) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, pursuant to Article 17a(3) of Regulation (EEC) No 2261/84, not more than eight months after the end of the marketing year the quantity actually produced in respect of which entitlement to the aid has been recognised must be determined; whereas, to that end in accordance with Article 12a of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3061/84 (6), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 2455/97 (7), the Member States concerned must notify the Commission, not later than 31 May following each marketing year, of the quantity recognised as qualifying for the aid in each Member State; whereas as a result of those communications the quantity eligible for aid for the 1996/97 marketing year amounts to 410 000 tonnes for Italy, 2 360 tonnes for France, 494 218 tonnes for Greece, 986 700 tonnes for Spain and 37 000 tonnes for Portugal; </inglise>
<eesti> vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 artikli 17a l&otilde;ikele 3 tuleb hiljemalt kaheksa kuu jooksul p&auml;rast turustusaasta l&otilde;ppu kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata tegelikult toodetud kogused, mille puhul on tunnustatud abi saamise &otilde;igust; selleks peavad asjaomased liikmesriigid vastavalt komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 (6) (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2455/97 (7)) artiklile 12a teatama komisjonile hiljemalt j&auml;rgmise turustusaasta 31. maiks kogused, mida on igas liikmesriigis tunnustatud kui toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavaid; k&otilde;nealuse teavitamise tulemusena on toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavad kogused 1996/97. turustusaastal Itaalia puhul 410 000 tonni, Prantsusmaa puhul 2 360 tonni, Kreeka puhul 494 218 tonni, Hispaania puhul 986 700 tonni ja Portugali puhul 37 000 tonni; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas recognition by the Member States of those quantities as qualifying for the aid implies that the checks referred to in Regulations (EEC) No 2261/84 and (EEC) No 3061/84 have been carried out; whereas, however, fixing actual production in accordance with the information on the quantities recognised as qualifying for Community aid by the Member States does not prejudge the conclusions that may be drawn from verification of the accuracy of that information under the clearance of accounts procedure; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuste koguste tunnustamine liikmesriikide poolt toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavatena eeldab m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 2261/84 ja m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 3061/84 osutatud kontrollide l&auml;biviimist; tegeliku toodangu kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramine vastavalt teabele koguste kohta, mida liikmesriigid on tunnustanud &uuml;henduse toetuse saamise tingimustele vastavatena, ei piira raamatupidamisarvestuse kontrollimise ja heakskiitmise k&auml;igus k&otilde;nealuse teabe &otilde;igsuse kontrollimise tulemusena tehtavaid v&otilde;imalikke j&auml;reldusi; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of the quantity actually produced, the unit amount of the production aid provided for in point (b) of the fifth subparagraph of Article 5(1) of Regulation No 136/66/EEC should also be fixed; </inglise>
<eesti> pidades silmas tegelikult toodetud koguseid, tuleks samuti kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata m&auml;&auml;ruse nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 viienda l&otilde;igu punktis b etten&auml;htud tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Oils and Fats, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> For the 1996/97 marketing year for olive oil: </inglise>
<eesti> 1996/97. turustusaastal on oliivi&otilde;li puhul: </eesti>
<inglise> - the quantity actually produced in respect of which entitlement to the production aid has been recognised and which is eligible for reimbursement by the EAGGF Guarantee Section is 1 930 278 tonnes, </inglise>
<eesti> - tegelikult toodetud kogus, mida on tunnustatud kui tootmistoetuse tingimustele vastavat ja mis vastab Euroopa P&otilde;llumajanduse Arendus- ja Tagatisfondi tagatisrahastu h&uuml;vitise saamise tingimustele, 1 930 278 tonni, </eesti>
<inglise> - the unit amount of the production aid shall be ECU 99,44 per 100 kilograms. </inglise>
<eesti> - tootmistoetuse m&auml;&auml;r &uuml;hiku kohta 99,44 ek&uuml;&uuml;d 100 kilogrammi kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 10 July 1998. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 10. juulil 1998 </eesti>
